{"tid":2197002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八達通：租用版成人八達通3年無用　下月1日起將收取15元行政費","createTime":"2020-09-10T09:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T16:02:20.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":288,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0b851ee92d0e73bdb5728cada2444f74aabc9ef6","tid":2197002,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"八達通公司表示，10月1日起將收取「不常用八達通行政費」。如果客戶持有「租用版成人八達通」，並於3年內無增值或作支付用途，「不常用八達通行政費」。若之後仍然沒有任何交易，則會每12個月被收取港幣15元，直至該八達通的餘額（如有）及按金被扣完為止。<br />\n<br />\n該公司表示，客戶只需在3年內進行1次八達通增值或付款交易，或退回該八達通，則不會被收取「不常用八達通行政費」。公司又指，上述措施目的是鼓勵客戶恒常使用其八達通，如無需要使用可退還，取回餘額退款。"},{"pid":"405c0cc2500b43780db57b6c7a4b2d487cf51019","tid":2197002,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1599730377406&amp;issue=20200910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1599730377406%26issue%3D20200910&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=5f8047e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1599730377406%26issue%3D20200910&h=2883e7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1599730377406&amp;issue=20200910</a>"},{"pid":"9ca54904b30669d99e16cc71634813dbacebbdfb","tid":2197002,"uid":19213,"like":250,"dislike":2,"score":248,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"買佢張八達通個陣有講過?"},{"pid":"49ef44d269c88a25d30dbcfa3207fc5076d91c5b","tid":2197002,"uid":121580,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"屋企有幾張舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e29b927db1d5ac35b384b519631cf9b41acd6ac","tid":2197002,"uid":241171,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"不思進取的垃圾 重要整衰多錢重"},{"pid":"0dd490ca986f0324c56df66bd19df10f1a2f4d